E-02 THE ISSUE DEPARTMENT IS INCORRECT.
E-03THE ISSUE DEPARTMENT IS NOT IN THE BY-TIME CALCULATION BIN M/F
E-04 REQUIRED FIELD.
E-05 THIS BIN DOES NOT EXIST.
E-06 THE PREVIOUS    BIN HAS NOT UNDERGONE RECEIVED-MESSAGE PROCESSING.
E-07 THIS BIN IS NOT IN THE BY-TIME CALCULATION BIN M/F.
E-08 THIS BIN HAS NOT BEEN PREPARED.
E-09 THIS BIN IS BEING PREPARED.
E-10 THIS BIN HAS BEEN PROCESSED.
E-11 THIS BIN IS NOT IN THE ALL-FACTORY BY-TIME CALCULATION BIN M/F.
E-12 THERE IS NO KANBAN DATA OF THE DATE-BIN.
